-Awak berempat ikut saya, cepat!
-Jom!

971
01:22:11,720 --> 01:22:13,930
-Ayuh, cepat!
-Cepat. Jalan!

972
01:22:24,650 --> 01:22:26,520
-Dia masih hidup.
-Scott, bawa dia keluar.

973
01:22:26,570 --> 01:22:27,820
Awak mesti... Tidak!

974
01:22:33,950 --> 01:22:35,120
Kita selamat!

975
01:22:57,470 --> 01:22:58,560
Yang terakhir.

976
01:23:00,390 --> 01:23:03,560
Periksa betul-betul
